title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may catch a glimpse of inspiration from unusual things, unique people, or exotic places. You might see an object from a distant land that captures your imagination, prompting you to dream of traveling far to experience what you fantasize. Its equally possible that you meet someone who shares remote ideas and insights with you today. Or you simply sample a different kind of cuisine. You dont necessarily have to like all you try or hear. But your willingness to embrace the unfamiliar brings you closer to the unity of spirit in humanity. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
